I Santo '''Domingo Savio''' o Saint '''Dominic Savio''' ([[w:Italian Language|Italianu]]: ''Domenico Savio''; [[Abril 2]], [[1842]] - [[w:March 9|Marzo 9]], [[1857]])<ref>SalesianVocation.com:[http://www.salesianvocation.com/saviobio.htm Biography of St.Dominic Savio]; Retrieved on [[24 November]], [[2006]].</ref>)<ref>SantieBeati.it:[http://www.santiebeati.it/dettaglio/32300 San Domenico Savio Adolescente]; Retrieved on [[24 November]], [[2006]]. </ref>  metung yang kayanakan a estudianti nang [[Giovanni Melchiorre Bosco|San Juan Bosco]] o Don Bosco. Manigaral yang mag-[[pari]] aniang mesakit ya at mete, mapaliaring uling king [[w:pleurisy]].<ref>BoscoNet.aust.com: [http://www.bosconet.aust.com/pdf/MOpart1.pdf ''Memoirs of the Oratory of Saint Francis de Sales'' by St. John Bosco (footnote 19, Chapter 6)]; Retrieved on [[24 November]], [[2006]]. </ref>

Matas ya paglalawe kaya ing kayang mestru, i [[w:Saint|San]] [[Giovanni Melchiorre Bosco|Juan Bosco]], a yang sinulat king talambie na, ''Ing Bie nang Domingo Savio'' (''Vita del giovanetto Domenico Savio''). Kayabe ya ing librung ita kareng aliwa pang kasulatan a meging batayan king kayang [[w:canonisation|pangasantu]]. Lipat ning king palage da reng dakal a taung masiadu yang anak king edad (labing apat a banua) bang magawang santu, mituring yang karapatdapat para kaniting alang kayanting dangalan uli ning "[[heroic virtue|mala-bayaning kayapan]]" king kayang pang aldo-aldong bie.<ref>stthomasirondequoit.com:[http://www.stthomasirondequoit.com/SaintsAlive/id752.htm Saints Alive: St. Dominic Savio]; Retrieved on [[November 24]], [[2006]]</ref> Ya kabud ing santu king anti kanitang edad, kayabe ne i [[Maria Goretti]] at Pontico ning Lyons<ref>EarlyChristianWritings.com: [http://www.earlychristianwritings.com/viennalyons.html Letter from Vienna and Lyons]; Retrieved on [[November 24]], [[2006]]</ref>, a mibulalag a santu e uling king panga-[[w:martyr|martir]], nun e uling mebie yang banal. Mi[[Canonization|bulalag]] yang santu kanitang Junio 12, 1954 kapamilata'nang [[w:Pope Pius XII|Papa Pio XII]].<ref>CatholicForum.org:[http://www.catholic-forum.com/SAINTS/saintd05.htm Dominic Savio]; Retrieved on [[24 November]], [[2006]].</ref>
Uli na niti ya ing anak diling e [[martyr|martir]] a meging santu king [[w:Roman Catholic Church|Iglesia Catolica]].<ref>DonBosco-torino.it:[http://www.donbosco-torino.it/eng/page5.html Main Altars in the Church]; Retrieved on [[November 24]], [[2006]]</ref> 

